{"word":"Rabbi","slug":"rabbi","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Rabbi</b> The title of a teacher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=8'>Mat 23:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=2'>Joh 3:2</a><br/> Ostentatiously used by the Pharisees<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=7'>Mat 23:7</a><br/> Used in addressing John<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=26'>Joh 3:26</a><br/> Used in addressing Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=38'>Joh 1:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=49'>Joh 1:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=2'>Joh 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=25'>Joh 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=25'>Mat 26:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=49'>Mat 26:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=5'>Mar 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=11&verse=21'>Mar 11:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=45'>Mar 14:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=31'>Joh 4:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=9&verse=2'>Joh 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=8'>Joh 11:8</a><br/> Jesus called Rabboni<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=51'>Mar 10:51</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=20&verse=16'>Joh 20:16</a><br/> Forbidden by Jesus as a title to His disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=8'>Mat 23:8</a>"}]}